headline: CME Group and LPGA Sign Two-Year Extension of CME Group Tour Championship with Largest Single Prize in Women's Golf
summary: The Ladies Professional Golf Association (LPGA) and CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced an extension of the CME Group Tour Championship and the season-long Race to the CME Globe through 2027. Since assuming title sponsorship of the LPGA Tour's season-ending tournament in 2011, CME Group has consistently grown its support, becoming one of the world's most prominent sponsors of women's sports.
